        {
          "insert": "\"some-id\"",
          "attributes": {
            "code": true
          }
        },
        {
          "insert": ") for objects that do not appear in the tree. On parse, duplicate texts get unique internal engine ids; that uniquification is an implementation detail that never appears in serialized output (the fitter always emits unique names today)."
        }
